comments: Durant (BKN) jumps from A to B into the body of Green (DEN) and affects his shot attempt at the rim.
Porter Jr. (DEN) makes contact to Durant's (BKN) arm that affects his jump shot attempt.
Griffin (BKN) makes contact to Jokic's (DEN) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Green (BKN) is a progressing player and legally takes two steps into his jump shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) jumps into Griffin (BKN) and makes contact to his arm, dislodging him from his rebounding position.
Harris (BKN) is late to the spot and makes contact to Jokic's (DEN) arm and body that affects his shot attempt.
Green (DEN) is in a legal guarding position defending Durant (BKN) on the perimeter.
Durant (BKN) briefly dribbles the ball off of his own side but he does not pin it to his body and bring it to a pause.
Durant (BKN) keeps his right arm in a legal position and marginal contact occurs when Durant briefly places his left hand on Jokic's (DEN) left arm before his shot attempt in the post.
Campazzo (DEN) and Griffin (BKN) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
Cancar (DEN) commits a take foul on Durant (BKN).
Claxton (BKN) briefly has an arm in Jokic's (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs that does not affect his FOM.
Green (BKN) gets his hand on the ball as Jokic (DEN) attempts to hand it off to Porter Jr. (DEN) and any contact before the held ball is incidental.
Claxton (BKN) moves toward Jokic (DEN) and marginal contact occurs as Jokic brings his left arm into Claxton as he retreats his arm into a vertical position.
Rivers (DEN) commits a take foul on Durant (BKN).
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
